@startuml
title 订阅工作流 - 时间驱动图
participant "计时器 / TTL" as Clock
participant "SubscriptionWorkflow" as Workflow

== refresh 周期 ==
Clock -> Workflow : refresh_sec 到期
Workflow -> Workflow : reconcile_subscriptions(timer)

== signal 临时订阅 ==
Clock -> Workflow : signal ttl 递减
Workflow -> Workflow : collect_active_signal_symbols

== stale 退订 ==
Clock -> Workflow : stale_ttl_sec 到期
Workflow -> Workflow : 判断是否 unsubscribe
@enduml
